<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFrameworks>net9.0;net8.0;net472</TargetFrameworks>
    <ImplicitUsings>disable</ImplicitUsings>
    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>
    <LangVersion>9.0</LangVersion>

    <!-- NuGet Package Metadata -->
    <Version>1.1.0</Version>
    <Authors>Ranni</Authors>
    <Description>一套通用的可回滚、可比较的快照组件，用于保存对象状态、生成差异（Diff），并支持高维数组、复杂对象结构。</Description>
    <Copyright>Copyright (c) Ranni 2026</Copyright>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://github.com/angleyanalbedo/SnapshotManager</PackageProjectUrl>
    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/angleyanalbedo/SnapshotManager.git</RepositoryUrl>
    <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
    <PackageTags>snapshot, diff, undo, redo, versioning, history, state-management</PackageTags>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>
- Feat: 新增对多个 .NET 框架 (net9.0, net8.0, net472) 的支持。
- Fix: 解决了各种编译错误和可空引用类型警告。
- Build: 将项目文件升级到现代 SDK 风格并改进了包元数据。
    </PackageReleaseNotes>

	<PackageLicenseFile>LICENSE.txt</PackageLicenseFile>
	<PackageReadmeFile>README.md</PackageReadmeFile>
  </PropertyGroup>
  <ItemGroup>
    <PackageReference Include="System.Text.Json" Version="10.0.5" Condition="'$(TargetFramework)' == 'net472'" />
  </ItemGroup>
  <ItemGroup>
      <None Include="../LICENSE.txt" Pack="true" PackagePath="\" />
      <None Include="../README.md" Pack="true" PackagePath="\" />
  </ItemGroup>

</Project>
